title: Blazing 5 – Week 8
itunes:title: Blazing 5 – Week 8
description:
Colin goes over his Blazing 5 picks with RJ Bell of Pregame.com and Fox Sports Radio who tells him which games the wise guys in Vegas agree or disagree with. Here are the games Colin and RJ go over:


Broncos @ Colts

Raiders @ Texans

Jets @ Jaguars

Giants @ Lions

Panthers @ 49ers


Plus, Colin reveals a 6th bonus pick exclusive to this podcast
